  "body": "In few places especially test fixtures, there is code like:\n\n```java\n\nSpecConfigEip4844.required(spec.forMilestone(SpecMilestone.EIP4844).getConfig());\n\nBeaconBlockBodySchemaEip4844.required(\n                spec.forMilestone(SpecMilestone.EIP4844)\n                    .getSchemaDefinitions()\n                    .getBeaconBlockBodySchema());\n\nspec.forMilestone(SpecMilestone.EIP4844)\n            .getConfig()\n            .toVersionEip4844()\n            .orElseThrow()\n```\n\nIt could be worth revisiting to see if there could be a way of simplifying the logic.\n\n",
